Package com.peaslimited.shoppeas.dto.mapper

Class WholesalerMapper

java.lang.Object
com.peaslimited.shoppeas.dto.mapper.WholesalerMapper
public class WholesalerMapper extends Object
Utility class responsible for mapping `WholesalerDTO`, `WholesalerAddressDTO`, `WholesalerAccountDTO`, and `ProductDetailedDTO` objects to their respective detail and profile DTO representations.

    • toDetailsDTO

      public static WholesalerDetailsDTO toDetailsDTO(WholesalerDTO wholesaler, WholesalerAddressDTO wholesalerAddress, List<ProductDetailedDTO> wholesalerProducts)
      Maps a WholesalerDTO, WholesalerAddressDTO, and a list of ProductDetailedDTO to a WholesalerDetailsDTO containing the wholesaler's details, address, and products.
      Parameters:
      wholesaler - The `WholesalerDTO` containing the basic information about the wholesaler.
      wholesalerAddress - The `WholesalerAddressDTO` containing the address of the wholesaler.
      wholesalerProducts - A list of `ProductDetailedDTO` objects representing the wholesaler's products.
      Returns:
      A `WholesalerDetailsDTO` combining the wholesaler's information, address, and products.

    • toProfileDTO

      public static WholesalerProfileDTO toProfileDTO(WholesalerDTO wholesaler, WholesalerAddressDTO wholesalerAddress, WholesalerAccountDTO wholesalerAccount)
      Maps a WholesalerDTO, WholesalerAddressDTO, and WholesalerAccountDTO to a WholesalerProfileDTO containing the wholesaler's profile information.
      Parameters:
      wholesaler - The `WholesalerDTO` containing the basic wholesaler information.
      wholesalerAddress - The `WholesalerAddressDTO` containing the address of the wholesaler.
      wholesalerAccount - The `WholesalerAccountDTO` containing the wholesaler's banking information.
      Returns:
      A `WholesalerProfileDTO` combining the wholesaler's information, account, and address.

    • toWholesalerProfileDTO

      public static WholesalerProductDetailsDTO toWholesalerProfileDTO(String swp_id, String wholesaler, String uen, String location, String postal_code, int duration, double distance, int stock, double price, double ratings)
      Maps product-related data such as product ID, wholesaler name, location, price, and ratings into a WholesalerProductDetailsDTO. This DTO represents detailed information about a specific product offered by a wholesaler.
      Parameters:
      swp_id - The unique identifier (wholesaler product id) for the product offered by the wholesaler.
      wholesaler - The name of the wholesaler.
      uen - The Unique Entity Number (UEN) of the wholesaler.
      location - The location of the wholesaler.
      postal_code - The postal code of the wholesalerâ€™s location.
      duration - The time taken to travel between the wholesaler and consumer.
      distance - The distance from the consumer to the wholesaler's location.
      stock - The current stock level of the product available.
      price - The price of the product.
      ratings - The average rating of the product.
      Returns:
      A `WholesalerProductDetailsDTO` object containing detailed information about a specific product.
